title: Rocket Power - Official Soundtrack
description:
The soundtrack album to Rocket Power was released on February 6, 2002. It is officially the soundtrack to the television film Rocket Power: Race Across New Zealand.

Rocket Power Soundtrack - Track Listing
=======================================
1. "Rocket Power Theme Song" by The Wipeouters (0:49)
2. "Individuality" by Area-7 (3:30)
3. "99 Red Balloons" by Goldfinger (3:51)
4. "Valentino" by Bowling for Soup (3:29)
5. "I'm Cool" by Reel Big Fish (1:41)

All audio files are encoded at 256Kbps (AAC) via iTunes.
